{"tid":1845871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"操普通話一家五口尖沙嘴酒店不適送院　男童救護車上嘔吐","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T13:03:31.000Z","uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ec1c2655d7f45315bc5dd047b8eb494cf6e713","tid":1845871,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200127/s00001/016a8a56a1a33e7b49e012a7ca1c3dc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200127%2Fs00001%2F016a8a56a1a33e7b49e012a7ca1c3dc2.jpg&h=d3195762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，一家五口操普通話的男女中有人感到不適，全數從尖沙嘴百樂酒店送抵伊利沙伯醫院。<br />\n<br />\n兩名成年男子、兩名成年女子及一名手抱男童，由兩輛救護車送抵醫院，車上救護員穿上全套保護衣，4名成年人全戴上口罩，其中一男一女戴上面罩。現場消息指出，該名手抱男童曾在救護車上嘔吐，現場所見他未有戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n5人經百樂酒店後門離開，出入口其後半落閘。酒店接待處職員及出入住客均戴上口罩，有清潔女工在場清潔。現場消息表示，有酒店住客感不適，自行電召救護車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200127/s00001/1580122092448/操普通話一家五口尖沙嘴酒店不適送院-男童救護車上嘔吐\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200127%2Fs00001%2F1580122092448%2F%E6%93%8D%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%8A%E5%98%94%E5%90%90&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=85e74506\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200127%2Fs00001%2F1580122092448%2F%E6%93%8D%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%8A%E5%98%94%E5%90%90&h=9a78ae72\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200127/s00001/1580122092448/操普通話一家五口尖沙嘴酒店不適送院-男童救護車上嘔吐</a>"},{"pid":"25aac26a18743e7b6ba268ee